</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_321" id="160r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Heinczen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Gich, gesezzen czü Melsendorf </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ew gesagt sey
                                <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz unser
                            <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> auf ew <expan>gehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> süllen, davon wissen wir nichts. Und als ir
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan> schreibt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Stephan Stüchsen, den <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> cze rede gesaczt, und der spricht
                        auch, er hab auf ew nicht <expan>gehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Het ir
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> mit <expan>dheine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> iht <expan>cze schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        wenn ir uns <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schribt</expan>, <add>mit wem ir <expan>cze
                                    schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> het und</add> was sache das were, so
                                <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> rede hören und ew
                            <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wissen lassen.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Laure<ex>n</ex>cii</expan>.</ab>
</div>
